<br>
Fact is, this board is seen by relatively few of the Quellious population.<br>
<br>
What you folks have is, a collection of guilds willing to help each other secure and camp the Ragefire spawn, and an open invitation for others to sign on and help and secure their own spot in that rotation.  That is very commendable and it's a great thing to have.  It will cut down on the conflicts with the camp.<br>
