I'm confused as to how making a fair list of people equates to monopolizing a spawn. Surely this is sharing it more, since with the extra help both the cleric currently camping Rage and the cleric in the list below can be at least semi-confident that they'll be able to take him down before another raid force marches in.<br>
<br>
